1
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:41,439
Hey, buddy

2
00:00:41,439 --> 00:00:42,560
You're Zhu Yihai, right?

3
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:45,280
My bro may have wronged your sister

4
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,359
But I can't let you touch my bro

5
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:49,679
Tonight at 8:30

6
00:00:50,039 --> 00:00:52,280
The old station, knives out.

7
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:55,079
How could I have seduced his sister?

8
00:00:59,119 --> 00:01:00,280
Spit it out, Zhu Yihai

9
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,119
When did you hook up with her?

10
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:04,239
I have no idea

11
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:05,319
Boss Lady

12
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,719
I've got amnesia, remember?

13
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:07,799
Can't remember a thing

14
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,359
You three, help me remember

15
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:15,480
What kind of guy was I before?

16
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:16,719
You?

17
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,680
Back in the day,

18
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:20,959
You were this kind of guy

19
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,200
In this city of Shanghai

20
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:33,560
The more ruthless, the higher you rise

21
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,760
Xu Wenqiang!

22
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,040
Yeah

23
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,480
You're way off the mark

24
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,000
Dali

25
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:44,920
You tell it

26
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,359
Me?

27
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:51,519
It was a dark and stormy night

28
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:54,439
Couldn't see your hand in front of you.

29
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,879
Hold it!

30
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,280
Sweetheart

31
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,560
Where you headed?

32
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,840
Why do creeps keep harassing me?

33
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,040
Let me tell you

34
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:09,560
We built this road.

35
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:11,599
We planted these trees.

36
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,680
If you want to pass,

37
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,400
leave your cash.

38
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,240
Yeah

39
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,240
Help!

40
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,680
Help!

41
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,360
Stop it!

42
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,120
Who goes there?

43
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,080
The Eagle-Shooting Hero

44
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,439
Zhu Yihai

45
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,159
Save me, brother!

46
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:32,280
Let that girl go!

47
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,560
Stop, stop, stop

48
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,520
That's nonsense

49
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,879
Okay, okay, just stop talking

50
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,159
Lili

51
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:43,080
You're so reliable, you tell it

52
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,800
Well, if you ask me

53
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,479
You're the most unreliable one.

54
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,560
What are you doing?

55
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:17,560
So who actually knows Li Erhu's sister?

56
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,240
I do.

57
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:26,520
Sun Qian, the Tangshan factory girl?

58
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,560
She used to tighten screws at Dongxing Factory.

59
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,080
Then after the factory went under,

60
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:32,800
she became a masseuse at Li Erhu's place.

61
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,599
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

62
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:47,319
Let's see what this old guy's taste is.

63
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,400
Who are you?

64
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,360
I'm Zhu Yihai.

65
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,120
Zhu Yihai?

66
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,600
I know him.

67
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,439
That's the Zhu Yihai from our factory.

68
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,519
I'll beat you to death!

69
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,360
Boss Hu said you're a sleazy bastard.

70
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,600
Turns out he was right!

71
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:36,959
Boss Hu wants to settle scores tonight.

72
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:38,759
And now you're coming after me?

73
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:39,720
Talk!

74
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:42,199
You trying to kidnap me?

75
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,680
To use me as leverage against Boss Hu?

76
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:53,000
Speak!

77
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,920
Dali.

78
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,639
What is it? What?

79
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:09,120
Look what time it is.

80
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,240
Bro Hai still isn't back.

81
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,000
Wait...

82
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,079
He hasn't come back yet?

83
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,519
I bet he went to face them alone!

84
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,360
No loyalty at all!

85
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:18,680
Let's go, call for backup!

86
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,680
Come on, save Bro Hai!

87
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,560
Feel good?

88
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,720
Try this one too.

89
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,480
Ow, ow, ow, ow!

90
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:41,160
With my skills...

91
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,720
I wasn't lying, was I?

92
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,720
I really did foot massage before.

93
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,199
I...

94
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:48,040
I believe you now.

95
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:51,360
So someone told you

96
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:54,000
that I ruined Dongxing Factory?

97
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,920
Right.

98
00:05:57,319 --> 00:06:00,199
So your bro Li Erhu

99
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:02,240
came looking to mess me up?

100
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,639
Right.

101
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,319
But the thing is, I had no idea!

102
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:18,360
Is this where the old man went down?

103
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,800
Damn it!

104
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:21,680
It's a trap!

105
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,319
Stop right there!

106
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:34,519
Stop!

107
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:37,759
What are you doing?

108
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,480
Going to a massage parlor alone?

109
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,240
Yeah.

110
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,560
It's not what you think.

111
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,680
Is it or isn't it?

112
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,360
I'm in a hurry, got things to do.

113
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,360
What "is it or isn't it"?

114
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,040
Zhu Yihai, what could you have to do?

115
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,160
Got money for a happy ending massage,

116
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,560
but no money to pay me back?

117
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:59,199
Zhu Yihai owes her money

118
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:04,879
and plans to skip out on it.

119
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,079
I wouldn't.

120
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,439
Then how do you plan to pay me back?

121
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:18,319
I gotta go or Zhu Yihai takes the fall.

122
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,639
We have a deal, okay?

123
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,480
Just promise me one thing.

124
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,079
Hurry it up.

125
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,120
I'm in a rush.

126
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,879
Hold on tight.

127
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:24,680
It's a bit fast!

128
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,160
Manager Xie, Manager Xie!

129
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,759
How's it going? Everything set?

130
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:41,920
Don't worry, Manager Xie.

131
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:44,079
I've already tipped off the Security Department.

132
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,759
The moment they throw a punch,

133
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:47,800
we'll haul them to the police station.

134
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,439
Once Zhu Yihai gets in a fight,

135
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:52,199
it won't just be a 15-day stint anymore.

136
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,519
Section Chief Dao, the net is set.

137
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:04,000
Good.

138
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,279
Put it down.

139
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,920
Boys, stay hidden.

140
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,160
Be ready to spring the trap.

141
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,120
Go.

142
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,639
Section Chief Dao, that's Affray.

143
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,920
Why don't we just call the cops?

144
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,959
Are you stupid?

145
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,639
If you call the cops directly,

146
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:23,279
where's the Security Department's credit?

147
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,920
No credit,

148
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,160
no promotion, no riches.

149
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:29,360
Brilliant!

150
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:29,759
Go.

151
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:30,920
Keep watching.

152
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:39,679
It's already past nine.

153
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,879
Zhu Yihai still isn't here?

154
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:43,000
Boss Hu, they've chickened out.

155
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,759
Ten more minutes,

156
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:47,399
and if that bastard still doesn't show,

157
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,879
we'll tear his pool hall apart!

158
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:52,480
Tear it up! Tear it up! Tear it up!

159
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,480
Tear who up, exactly?

160
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,799
Section Chief Dao, they're here!

161
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,200
Brothers, the moment they make a move,

162
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,320
take them all in.

163
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,600
Where's Bro Hai?

164
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,720
That big-headed Zhu Yihai isn't here.

165
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,480
So just you two small fry showed up?

166
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,519
You trying to scare me with Bro Hai?

167
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:29,639
What if I am?

168
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:31,360
You stinking busker.

169
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:32,679
What did he say?

170
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,039
He called you a busker.

171
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,639
In front of all these people?

172
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,919
That bastard.

173
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:53,720
Come on.

174
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,799
Give us a tune.

175
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:55,720
Get him!

176
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,399
Yes!

177
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:57,440
Brothers,

178
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,799
take him down, take him down!
